Hello everyone.

00:00:00.710 --> 00:00:02.780
Welcome to another
Authors at Google talk.

00:00:02.780 --> 00:00:05.050
Today we have Nick Offerman
to talk about his book

00:00:05.050 --> 00:00:06.632
"Paddle Your Own Canoe."

00:00:06.632 --> 00:00:08.340
He's going to start
off with a few songs,

00:00:08.340 --> 00:00:09.640
and then we're going
to discuss the book

00:00:09.640 --> 00:00:10.896
and open it up to questions.

00:00:17.305 --> 00:00:19.390
NICK OFFERMAN: Thank you.

00:00:19.390 --> 00:00:23.623
Good afternoon, Google.

