rainbow for her birthday.

00:00:52.260 --> 00:00:54.410
And I said, thank you honey.

00:00:54.410 --> 00:00:55.410
That should be easy.

00:00:55.410 --> 00:00:57.740
And I made a few calls.

00:00:57.740 --> 00:00:59.287
NBC was no help whatsoever.

00:01:02.331 --> 00:01:04.580
And then I realized I could
make a rainbow out of art.

00:01:04.580 --> 00:01:06.650
So this is the
first song I wrote.

00:01:06.650 --> 00:01:13.650
And my friend CornMo.com
helped me set it to chords.

00:01:13.650 --> 00:01:16.525
And he's much more
entertaining than I am.

00:01:16.525 --> 00:01:19.420
Please avail yourself
of his talents.

00:01:19.420 --> 00:01:20.310
"The Rainbow Song."

00:01:20.310 --> 00:01:22.101
[MUSIC - NICK OFFERMAN,
