00:04:11.645 --> 00:04:17.480
NICK OFFERMAN: I posed
for that font in 1996.

00:04:17.480 --> 00:04:20.924
And I've been in
the ocean since.

00:04:20.924 --> 00:04:24.031
I have two big-screen
TVs, both with shots

00:04:24.031 --> 00:04:30.818
of all of you in case I need
some perspective, apparently.

00:04:34.680 --> 00:04:43.610
Looking at you this way is
too daunting, so-- what else

00:04:43.610 --> 00:04:45.740
do I do?

00:04:45.740 --> 00:04:48.000
My friend Corn Mo,
actually, suggested to me

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:53.570
