all with woodworking themes.

00:04:53.570 --> 00:05:00.840
And we laughed, quaffed our
seventh beer at McSorley's Pub.

00:05:00.840 --> 00:05:04.690
And then I said, wait a second.

00:05:04.690 --> 00:05:06.860
I like the sound of that.

00:05:06.860 --> 00:05:13.190
And so this is the first song
from that forthcoming album.

00:05:13.190 --> 00:05:15.780
It's very much in progress,
but this is just a taste.

00:05:31.470 --> 00:05:34.056
Thank you to Kristie for
loaning me her guitar.

00:05:34.056 --> 00:05:37.437
Mine arrived broken.

00:05:37.437 --> 00:05:38.886
This one is cute as shit.

