00:10:27.658 --> 00:10:29.770
INTERVIEWER: So
welcome to Google.

00:10:29.770 --> 00:10:33.080
Thanks for indulging us with
song and a little bit of dance

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:33.580
as well.

00:10:33.580 --> 00:10:35.538
NICK OFFERMAN: Thank you
